e belonged to him,' said Linda in confidential tones, showing the pistol to her sister.

'The flashlight too?'

'No, that's Mac's.'

'My!' said Mariette reverently touching the huge leathery thing.

One of the youths, propelled by Krug, collided with the umbrella stand.

'Now, now, will you please stop this unseemly scuffle,' said Mac pulling Krug back (poor Krug executed a cakewalk). The two youths at once made for the nursery.

